This repository bundles or vendors the following third-party works:

1. rhwp (external/rhwp, git submodule) — MIT License
   Copyright (c) 2025-2026 Edward Kim
   Used as a PARSE-ONLY bootstrap for the binary .hwp (HWP5) format and as
   a layout reference; rendering always happens from tf-hwp's own IR.
   https://github.com/kwakseongjae/rhwp (mirror fork)

2. Nanum Gothic / Nanum Myeongjo fonts (assets/fonts/) — SIL Open Font
   License 1.1 (assets/fonts/OFL.txt)
   Copyright (c) NAVER Corporation. Bundled as the redistributable default
   screen/PDF faces. Every font in the curated catalog (docs/FONT-CATALOG.md)
   is OFL.

3. hwp-oracle (crates/hwp-oracle) shells out to LibreOffice + the
   H2Orestart import filter (GPL) strictly OUT-OF-PROCESS via the `soffice`
   CLI as an optional, native-only fidelity *reference*. No GPL code is
   linked into or distributed with tf-hwp binaries or npm packages.

4. Sample/benchmark documents (benchmarks/, corpus/) are publicly
   distributed Korean government application forms and format-conformance
   test files (including files from the rhwp test corpus) used solely for
   regression testing of the parser/typesetter.
